    {
      "page_slug": "index",
      "zone": "main",
      "scope": "page",
      "section_type": "custom",
      "config": {
        "html": "<h1>WELCOME TO THE BMW CAR CLUB CANBERRA</h1>\n  <p>The BMW Car Club of Canberra (Formerly BMW Car Club ACT) was formed in 1985 and is one of the 9 Official BMW Car Clubs in Australia.</p>\n  <p>Part of a worldwide community of more than 200,000 members!</p>\n  <p>We are a not-for-profit club, fully insured and supported by BMW Clubs and Community Management and BMW AG.</p>\n  <p>The Club is made up of BMW (car and bike) enthusiasts brought together by one of the world's greatest motoring companies.</p>\n  <p>Our events take place in the ACT and surrounding areas including the South Coast and Southern Tablelands.</p>\n  <p>We also have events across the Eastern Seaboard with other Official BMW Clubs.</p>\n  <p>We actively support local businesses, community organisations and support local charities such as Marymead.</p>"
      },
      "position": 2,
      "visible": true,
      "column_span": "1"
    },
    {
      "page_slug": "index",
